    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >I Have More Hours Than You: The Game</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game was designed with a simple idea in mind: Hours.<br>You are thrown into an abyss with nothing to keep you company, other than your thoughts and the occasional abnormal event.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Events</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056640/extras/f22bb00353404f8c948984eb68c2bf76.poster.avif?t=1738819264\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056640/extras/f22bb00353404f8c948984eb68c2bf76.webm?t=1738819264\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056640/extras/f22bb00353404f8c948984eb68c2bf76.mp4?t=1738819264\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Legend has it that these abnormal events may be interacted with in some way. But it's up to you to find out.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Achievements</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056640/extras/3f8f6f9017ee998343a78d1e6975d726.poster.avif?t=1738819264\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056640/extras/3f8f6f9017ee998343a78d1e6975d726.webm?t=1738819264\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056640/extras/3f8f6f9017ee998343a78d1e6975d726.mp4?t=1738819264\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Follow NULL's achievement journey through the void. You will periodically be given excerpts that tell an abstract story about acceptance.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Customization</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056640/extras/ca71dfcbd6e7e52cfd6b35407f57f5ef.poster.avif?t=1738819264\" width=600 height=136 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056640/extras/ca71dfcbd6e7e52cfd6b35407f57f5ef.webm?t=1738819264\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056640/extras/ca71dfcbd6e7e52cfd6b35407f57f5ef.mp4?t=1738819264\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >During your travels, you will acquire new mouse customisation options. Collect them all!</p>",
